//! BDD Behavioral Contract Verification for twerk-app
//!
//! This test suite verifies behavioral contracts using Given/When/Then
//! structure against the public API. Three lenses applied:
//! - **Liar Check**: Does the implementation match its claims?
//! - **Breakage Check**: What happens when conditions degrade?
//! - **Completeness Check**: Is every public item exercised?
//!
//! Generated by bdd-enforcer for bead tw-dji.

